lead_paragraph: Playmaker Juan Mata says he did not lose any sleep over Jose Mourinho's arrival at Manchester United despite longstanding and widespread rumours that the pair had fallen out when they were both at Chelsea.

headline.print_headline: Mata Says Had Nothing to Fear From Mourinho's Arrival at United
headline.main: Mata Says Had Nothing to Fear From Mourinho's Arrival at United
